"color:#be8100" target=3D"_blank">Fast Company</a>:</p>

<blockquote style=3D"background-color:#fafafa;color:#666;font-style:italic;=
margin-left:0;padding:20px 30px">
<p style=3D"color:#333">To ride out the storm, professionals of all generat=
ions appear to be turning to =E2=80=9Cportfolio careers=E2=80=9D to earn th=
eir living through a mix of contracted freelance jobs, consulting gigs, sho=
rt-term projects, board membership, and other engagements that allow them t=
o apply their expertise under flexible conditions.</p>
</blockquote>

<p style=3D"color:#333">Given that Generation X is already at a point where=
 ageist layoffs arise, job dissatisfaction is high, and disruptive automati=
on technologies are coming even faster due to COVID-19, we may <a href=3D"h=
ttps://t.dripemail2.com/c/eyJhY2NvdW50X2lkIjoiNDMxMTg3MCIsImRlbGl2ZXJ5X2lkI=
joidzRoZTlvMWQzMjM2ZzRwb253YTIiLCJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5mYXN0Y29tcGFueS5j=
