29udGVudD1UaGUrUmlzZStvZit0aGUrUGVyc29uYWwrRW50ZXJwcmlzZSJ9" rel=3D"noopene=
r noreferrer" style=3D"color:#be8100" target=3D"_blank">lead the charge</a>=
 away from traditional employment arrangements:</p>

<blockquote style=3D"background-color:#fafafa;color:#666;font-style:italic;=
margin-left:0;padding:20px 30px">
<p style=3D"color:#333">With stronger levels of dissatisfaction building be=
fore COVID-19, it is safe to assume that this crisis may push Gen-Xers, in =
particular, to steer their careers in a new direction. According to data fr=
om BMO Wealth Management, 50% of Gen-Xers who have portfolio careers cite =
=E2=80=9Chaving autonomy and control=E2=80=9D as a top motivator for self-e=
mployment=E2=80=94the highest of all generations.</p>
</blockquote>

<p style=3D"color:#333">Another way to think about a =E2=80=9Cportfolio car=
eer=E2=80=9D is the <em>personal enterprise</em>. The term was coined in th=
e book <a href=3D"https://t.dripemail2.com/c/eyJhY2NvdW50X2lkIjoiNDMxMTg3MC=
IsImRlbGl2ZXJ5X2lkIjoidzRoZTlvMWQzMjM2ZzRwb253YTIiLCJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL2Fte=
