means that the key to navigating the coming economy is to live an <em>entre=
preneurial life</em>.</p>

<p style=3D"color:#333">His use of =E2=80=9Centrepreneurial=E2=80=9D is a b=
it different than you may be thinking. Taneja is a venture capitalist who s=
ees most full-time jobs disappearing (even if the pandemic didn=E2=80=99t h=
appen), replaced by just-in-time contractual talent that operates via enhan=
ced technology.</p>

<p style=3D"color:#333">Instead of a crafting a resume to land a single emp=
loyer, Taneja sees a mix of long-term contracts, freelance projects, side h=
ustles, and entrepreneurial products that you develop and market with the a=
id of the AI and automation that once threatened to replace you.</p>

